fields.descriptive_line: Glass-blowers' pattern-book containing design (1595) for wine glasses, goblets, tumblers, decanters, tazzas and cruet sets etc.  322 pages of tracing paper, with 4 laid endpapers, one watermarked 1895, full-bound in leather.  From the Venice and Murano Glass Co. Ltd., London.
